<section class="about-three how-to-give-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-start">
            <div class="section-title text-left">
                <span class="section-title__tagline editable">Community Foundation of Teton Valley</span>
                <h2 class="section-title__title editable">How To Give Through The Tin Cup Challenge</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-three__left">
                    
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">During the Giving Period each summer, you can give as a community donor or a Challenger. Community donors make a single designated gift, with their chosen amounts allocated to specific nonprofits they wish to support. Challengers and Friends of the Challenge provide undesignated funding to partially match the designated gifts of community donors, substantially increasing the impact of each participating organization's fundraising efforts.</p>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">As a Tin Cup Donor, making direct designated gifts:</p>
                    <ol class="about-three__list">
                        <li class="editable">100% of your donation goes to the nonprofits of your choice.</li>
                        <li class="editable">Provide funding to promote and support the charitable mission of your organizations.</li>
                        <li class="editable">Simplify giving by making a single payment to the Community Foundation of Teton Valley on behalf of local nonprofits.</li>
                    </ol>
                    <p class="about-three__text-3 editable">Both ways of giving are intrinsic to our philanthropic model.</p>
                    <a href="/nonprofits/" class="thm-btn about-three__btn editable">View All Nonprofits</a>
                </div>
