<section class="about-three in-kind-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-three__left">
                    <div class="section-title text-left">
                        <span class="section-title__tagline editable">Community Foundation of Teton Valley</span>
                        <h2 class="section-title__title editable">Our Tin Cup Challenger Giving</h2>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="about-three__subtitle editable">Six Weeks Of Giving</h3>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">During the 6-week Tin Cup giving period, donors give directly to their favorite local nonprofits — knowing their gifts will be partially matched by our Challenger Fund.</p>
                    <p class="about-three__text-1 editable">Challengers are generous individuals and businesses who contribute $1,500 or more. Their support not only increases the impact of every gift but also funds the Foundation's Competitive Grants, Youth Philanthropy Program, and nonprofit workshops, ensuring year-round impact.</p>
                    <p class="about-three__text-3 editable">Thanks to Challengers, 100% of every designated gift goes to nonprofits, plus a powerful match that multiplies community generosity.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="thm-btn about-three__btn editable">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="about-three__right">
                    <div class="about-three__img-box wow slideInRight" data-wow-delay="100ms" data-wow-duration="2500ms">
                        <div class="about-three__img">
                            <img src="/assets/images/tin-cup/nonprofit-booths.jpg" alt="Tin Cup Challenger Giving" class="editable" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="about-three__border"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
